<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l4">vvie daʒ ewr hauptleute cʒu Manheim Jm vnd dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l5"><expan>Eb<ex>erhard</ex></expan> <expan>Grefemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> auch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . Acht wegen mit <expan>vveliſche<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l6">weine cʒu Monheim aufgehalten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l7"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden mit <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ ewrn hauptleuten <expan>ſchicke<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l8">vnd beſtellen wöllet / durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> vvıllıgen dinſt willen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_210_r1l10">daʒ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_210_line_1577132973210_947">ſie </ab></add> den <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
